~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : hangman                                   ~FTRNUTS Version 3.0.2
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : hangman <start/stop/status>

   This allows you to start/stop/status the progress of your game 
   of Hangman.  You currently can play this game by yourself; maybe 
   someday we can get it modded to allow more than one user to 
   play at a time.  Until then, live with it :P ;)


